        <name>XCsiSs_ConfigTable</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>MIPI CSI Rx Subsystem configuration table (SDT) </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This table contains configuration information for each MIPI CSI Rx Subsystem instance in the system when using System Device Tree (SDT). Each entry describes the hardware configuration for a specific instance including sub-core presence and parameters. </para>        </detaileddescription>
